data.description:
Attention UCBMFET:

We thank you for your cooperation and patience these past 24+ hours. In a few short moments, posts will no longer be subject to approval. 

From now until December 16th, the moderating team will not be readily addressing most of your concerns. This may come a shock to some of you but, the UCBMFET team (with the exception of Chris Tril) is human. We, like many of you, are also students with finals to study for, and we do not get paid to regulate a Facebook group with 36K+ members, so please bear with us. If outrageous shit gets posted, and we do not address it in .02 seconds as we normally do, please understand that we do have more important things than correcting the idiocies of our more edgy posters. 

With that said, we kindly ask that you try your best at not being absolute shitheads to one another and posting disrespectful content to specific individuals or particular groups of individuals.So have fun and don't spend too much time on this cancerous Facebook group when you should be studying for finals.

—This message has been brought to you by Sizzler™(Now You're Talking) and the administrative and moderating team of UC Berkeley Memes for Edgy Teens

P.S.: "As a member of the Greek..." memes are getting old at an absurdly rapid pace.
